title: Match facts: PSG v Real Madrid (UEFA Champions League)
text:
Full time: PSG 0-0 Real Madrid
Yellow cards:
Matuidi, Verratti, Aurier (PSG)
Ramos, Cheryshev (Real Madrid)
Line-ups
PSG: Kevin Trapp, Thiago Silva, Marquinhos, Maxwell, Serge Aurier, Marco Verratti, Thiago Motta, Blaise Matuidi, Edinson Cavani (Javier Pastore 66), Zlatan Ibrahimovic, Angel Di Maria (Lucas 66)
Real Madrid: Keylor Navas, Raphael Varane, Sergio Ramos, Marcelo, Danilo, Toni Kroos, Casemiro, Lucas Vazquez, Isco (Luka Modric 69), Cristiano Ronaldo, Jese Rodriguez (Denis Cheryshev 73)
Venue: Parc des Princes (Paris)
Referee: N. Rizzoli (Italy)
